Package: LoGloBias
Type: Package
Title: Calculates bias scores from standardised local-global bias data
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Felix Schweigkofler
Maintainer: Felix Schweigkofler <felixschweigkofler@gmail.com>
Description: A package to work in a standardised way with data from local-global bias experiments.
    Exclude trials or participants based on different parameters.
    Calculate summary statistics from trial-level data.
    Calculate scores from summary-level data.
    Correlate scores with each other.
    Calculate statistics of summary-level data or score-level data.
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports: dplyr
RoxygenNote: 7.3.1
